6. Also allow the user the ability to resize the size of Output (sometimes the image in the terminal output is far too large and you only see a small section), do not automatically resize, how it is already done is perfectly fine, however let the user extend the size of the output vertically and horizontally, the block should follow in expanding horizontally only (meaning the code (10 lines) and the title, etc stay the same)